d, Sai and Shuriken"), ''[[Danny Phantom]]'' (Bertrand), ''[[Digimon Savers]]'' (Falcomon), ''[[Eon Kid]]'' (Black Beauty and her ninja robot army), ''[[Family Guy]]'' (in "[[Wasted Talent]]" and "[[I Take Thee Quagmire]]"), ''[[Happy Tree Friends]]'' (Generic Tee Ninjas), ''[[Jackie Chan Adventures]]'' (the Shadowkhan), ''[[Johnny Test]]'' (one of Johnny's transformation is Ninja Johnny), ''[[Kim Possible]]'' (the Yamanouchi ninja school), ''[[The Legend of Prince Valiant]]'' ("The Ghost"),<ref>{{cite web |url=http://valarnrow.i8.com/EpisodeSummaries.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070503134354/http://valarnrow.i8.com/EpisodeSummaries.html |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2007-05-03 |title=Episode Summaries |publisher=Valarnrow.i8.com |date= |accessdate=2013-08-04 |df= }}</ref> ''[[The Legend of Zelda (TV series)|The Legend of Zelda]]'' (Sing), ''[[The Penguins of Madagascar]]'' ("Mental Hen/Siege the Day" and "Street Smarts/Nighty Night Ninja"), ''[[Phineas and Ferb]]'' ("What a Croc!/Ferb TV"), ''[[Planet Sketch]]'' (Ninja Handyman),<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.planetsketch.com/archive/character_ninja.html |title=Ninja Handyman |publisher=Planet Sketch |date= |accessdate=2013-08-04}}</ref> ''[[The Real Adventures of Jonny Quest]]'' ("Night of the Zinja"),{{Citation needed|date=January 2018}} ''[[Robot Chicken]]'', ''[[Road Rovers]]'' ("Let Sleeping Dogs Lie"), ''[[Samurai Jack]]'' ("Samurai versus Ninja"), ''[[The Simpsons]]'' (in "[[The Telltale Head]]" [[Bart Simpson]] disguises as a ninja; in "[[Treehouse of Horror XVIII]]" one of the aliens is dressed as a ninja, in "[[Husbands and Knives]]" the [[Comic Book Guy]] has ninja weapons, and in "[[Yokel Chords]]" Bart plays a spoof [[video game]] with a [[Mileena|female ninja]]), ''[[Skunk Fu]]'' (Ninja Monkeys), ''[[South Park]]'' ("[[Good Times with Weapons]]" and "[[Fantastic Easter Special]]"), ''[[Stroker and Hoop]]'' ("Ninja Worrier" and "Chopping Spree"),<ref>{{cite web|url=http://video.adultswim.com/stroker-and-hoop/ninja-worrier.html |title=Stroker and Hoop : Ninja Worrier - Adult Swim Gold Episodes |publisher=Web.archive.org |date= |accessdate=2016-02-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406064820/http://video.adultswim.com/stroker-and-hoop/ninja-worrier.html |archivedate=April 6, 2012 }}</ref> ''[[Superman: The Animated Series]]'' (Death Fist Ninja), ''[[Teen Titans]]'' (in "Masks", [[Beast Boy]] has a video game "Super Ninja Showdown 8"), ''[[List of Transformers TV series|The Transformers]]'' (Greatshot, Nightbird and [[Prowl (Transformers)|Prowl]]), ''[[The Venture Bros.]]'' (Otaku Senzuri), ''[[Wolverine and the X-Men (TV series)|Wolverine and the X-Men]]'' and ''[[Xiaolin Showdown]]'' (Tubbimura).
